▁there ▁is ▁here by ▁set ▁up ▁a ▁community ▁committee ▁for ▁the ▁farm ▁account ancy ▁data ▁network ▁, ▁here ina f ter ▁called ▁the ▁" ▁community ▁committee ▁" ▁.
