▁- ▁lay ▁down ▁guide ▁values ▁( ▁annex ▁ii ▁) ▁for ▁nitrogen ▁dioxide ▁in ▁the ▁atmosphere ▁in ▁order ▁to ▁improve ▁the ▁protection ▁of ▁human ▁health ▁and ▁contribute ▁to ▁the ▁long ▁- ▁term ▁protection ▁of ▁the ▁environment ▁.
