▁with ▁this ▁" ▁us ▁versus ▁them ▁" ▁view ▁of ▁the ▁world ▁, ▁it ▁was ▁not ▁hard ▁to ▁rally ▁voters ▁, ▁from ▁the ▁most ▁disen fr anch ised ▁all ▁the ▁way ▁up ▁to ▁the ▁sal ar ied ▁middle ▁class ▁- ▁- ▁more ▁than ▁enough ▁for ▁the ▁left ▁to ▁secure ▁electoral ▁majorities ▁.
